<p>
   The BlueJ development environment is a open-source application designed to help students learn to 
   program.  It has several features of professional development environments, but has left out
   many specialized ones.  It also has a unique class-based diagram frame to help with understanding
   of inheritance and other object-oriented issues. 
</p>
<p>For more information, go to <a href="http://bluej.org/">http://bluej.org</a></p>